        "last_activity_date": 1351048827,
        "creation_date": 1351048827,
        "body": "<p>The <code>RatingBar<\/code> widget should be placed in the list row layout that you use in the adapter, <code>R.layout.list_item<\/code>. Right now, you just placed a <code>RatingBar<\/code> widget below the <code>ListView<\/code> in the main layout.<\/p>\n",
